_sText:
Prefab made by ]ES[ Church Xx ]GaD[

To install extract the map to your mapsrc folder in source sdk content


To put it your map...

****All of these are Important. Read before opening****

Make the player clip in the middle divide the whole level by Ct's and T's (Resize it if your level is smaller or larger).

The Trigger blocks that cover the court are made to block the ball and not players from leaving the playing area. 

Removing is simple. Just remove the both trigger walls and their filters on top of the scoreboard

Make sure that the two triggers named hurtt and hurtct are placed and resized to their designated sides on the 

map. 

Make any changes you would like to the design of the map, but do not change any features of the scoreboard or any 

of the triggers unless you are absolutely sure of what you are doing. Do not rename triggers or they WILL NOT WORK 

CORRECTLY


I hope you guys can make some pretty cool maps with this design... My test design for this gameplay was named 

mg_BeachVolleyBall however this is a much more simple formulation for the game mode. Check it out and write on my 

profile if you have any questions on Gamebanana.com; My name is IChurchXxI.

ENJOY EVERYONE

Make some maps guys!
